CODING
------

No need to code anything, just point the authors to any missing Gaussian blur.


RELEASING
---------

To update the pypi hub, you need an account on pypi, and then run the following commands:

	# update version number on file setup.py
	# update version number on file gblurs.py
	python -m build
	python -m twine upload dist/gblurs-X-py3-none-any.whl
	rm -rf build dist gblurs.egg-info
